McCarthy and Stone Plc, a public U.K.Company which owns and operates retirement homes, has signed a100 mln stg multi-option facility, National Westminster BankPlc said as arranger.    The facility incorporate a 70 mln stg committed elementfrom a group of international banks.    The facility will provide the group with working capital tomeet its planned expansion in the U.K. Over the next threeyears. REUTER&#3;